high_descs: Turn around and face the counter where the toaster is.
Pick the tomato up from the counter.
Go to the right and turn to face the sink.
Put the tomato in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the tomato up.
Turn around and cross the room to stand in front of the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter top in front of you.
Pick up the tomato in front of the toaster, on the counter.
Turn to your right and go to the sink.
Place the tomato in the sink, turn the water on, rinse the tomato, turn the water off, and remove the tomato from the sink.
Turn to your left and go to the microwave, above the stove.
Place the tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the toaster on the counter to your right.
Grab the tomato in front of the toaster on the counter.
Turn right and walk to the sink to your left.
Place the tomato in the sink, wash it and remove from the sink.
Turn around and walk to the stove to your right and look up to the microwave.
Place the clean tomato inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean tomato inside the microwave.
